						<div class="postbody">In ca65 you can easily create striped arrays using .define, .lobytes, and .hibytes:<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; .define Things Thing0, Thing1, Thing2, Thing3<br /><br />ThingsLow:<br />&nbsp; .lobytes Things<br /><br />ThingsHigh:<br />&nbsp; .hibytes Things</div></div>

