						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">slembcke wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">As a random aside. This:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp; lda animation, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta sprite_ptr + 0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; lda animation, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta sprite_ptr + 1</div><br /><br />Can become this:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">&nbsp; &nbsp; lda animation + 0, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta sprite_ptr + 0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; lda animation + 1, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; sta sprite_ptr + 1</div></div><br /> Oh cool!  I'm gonna use this.</div>

