				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The . begins all control commands in ca65. See here: <a href="http://cc65.github.io/doc/ca65.html" class="postlink">http://cc65.github.io/doc/ca65.html</a><br /><br />If you .define a comma separated list, .lobytes is like .byte with &lt; before every element in that list, and .hibytes does the same but with &gt;. I don't find it's very usable for longer lists, but YMMV, and there's a bunch of other alternatives.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

